{
  "stem": "2578.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since the conditions were very bad in the ghetto, many Jews volunteered to leave the ghetto and to go to work someplace else, hoping that the conditions there will be better than the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Labor camps.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And these orders came in from time to time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the more they came in, the higher was the amount of the request.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From 1,000 people, they moved up to 1,500, to 2,000, to 5,000, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then it came a time when rumors started to come in to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As far as I know, I have no idea how they came in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they did come in, letting know the-- the Jews in the ghetto that in many cases the Jews that are being shipped out from the ghetto are not going to work that they were promised to, but they went to extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know about Auschwitz in those days, and we didn't know about Chelmno in those days, because the Lodz ghetto was extremely sealed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the beginning, we had newspapers come in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had clandestine radios.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But those that were caught with these things were shot on the spot or hanged, and the people had to watch them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So little by little, all these information means disappeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't have any knowledge whatsoever what's going on outside the ghetto, or in the world, or how the-- the war was progressing, and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no way of having any kind of information.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as opposed to different ghettos like Bialystok, or Warsaw, or any other ghettos, we had no contact whatsoever with the outside Gentile population.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did not help us in any way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have no contact with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did not have any communication whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
